ugust at 10:35 SA time.\", \"from\": 2544, \"to\": 2629, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's followed byRound 1at11:45.Sunday 04 August sees the semi-finals at 20:00and then thegrand final,where Simbine will hope to line up, at21:50.Do not miss it for the world, and do not you just love the Olympics?\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2845, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know by clicking on the comment tab below this article or emailinginfo@thesouthafrican.com.\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2945, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can also send a WhatsApp to 060 011 021 1.\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2992, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2966, \"end\": 2974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.9904660485989626, \"rank\": 0.00962572257220674, \"text\": \"WhatsApp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow@TheSAnews on XandThe South African on Facebookfor your social fix.\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 3066, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"WIN R2 000: Take The South African's SASSA Survey  The South African is hiring!\", \"from\": 3068, \"to\": 3147, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3068, \"end\": 3071, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"score\": 0.9999607455471483, \"rank\": 3.925126927612859e-05, \"text\": \"WIN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\"}, {\"begin\": 3072, \"end\": 3074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"score\": 0.9999679840139147, \"rank\": 3.1958065590370545e-05, \"text\": \"R2\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Freelance writing positions available  Follow The South African on 